Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
DALLAS CEDARS / INFILL INVESTMENT
“QUALIFIED ECONOMIC OPPORTUNITY ZONE” ; The properties at S. Good Latimer Parkway represent a unique opporunity to acquire two (2) strong industrial/flex assets totaling approximately 57,000 square feet on over a combined two acres of land in an area primed for future development and growth*. The two lots contain air conditioned showroom space and parking. The larger land area (Tract 1) of the two separate lots can also command higher rents should the new owner prefer to reposition the existing buildings for another use. Located just outside Downtown Dallas and The Cedars, with easy access to two major freeways, the Property can offer significan long term benefits within a growing area of Dallas, in a city with steady property demand, rental growth and appreciation. 
*Ownership will consider individual sale of either property.
